1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:03,640
(Episode 51)

2
00:00:07,310 --> 00:00:09,080
Thank you. Let's go.

3
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:20,490
That's my Jang Mi.

4
00:00:21,330 --> 00:00:24,100
My daughter Jang Mi is so pretty!

5
00:00:24,730 --> 00:00:26,600
- Jang Mi is pretty.
- Jang Mi.

6
00:00:26,660 --> 00:00:27,670
- Jang Mi.
- Jang Mi.

7
00:00:27,730 --> 00:00:29,330
- Jang Mi.
- Oh Jang Mi.

8
00:00:29,330 --> 00:00:31,870
- Jang Mi.
- Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

9
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:33,300
- Jang Mi.
- Jang Mi is pretty.

10
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:34,770
- You're my daughter.
- Oh Jang Mi.

11
00:00:34,770 --> 00:00:36,540
- Whatever they say, you're my daughter!
- Oh Jang Mi.

12
00:00:36,540 --> 00:00:37,610
Jang Mi.

13
00:00:41,610 --> 00:00:42,610
No.

14
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:46,950
(Name: Ma Seo Rin)

15
00:00:49,050 --> 00:00:50,160
"Ma Seo Rin?"

16
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,730
Ma Seo Rin!

17
00:01:15,610 --> 00:01:16,650
Ma Seo Rin!

18
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:29,860
Seo Rin.

19
00:01:30,530 --> 00:01:31,930
Ma Seo Rin.

20
00:01:31,930 --> 00:01:33,500
What happened to Seo Rin?

21
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:36,230
Seo Rin!

22
00:01:36,230 --> 00:01:37,770
Ma Seo Rin!

23
00:01:38,970 --> 00:01:40,540
We can't get caught right now.

24
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:43,480
If we get caught, it's all for nothing.

25
00:01:43,810 --> 00:01:45,610
Oh Jang Mi, just get through tonight.

26
00:01:46,210 --> 00:01:49,080
Otherwise, I'm dead. I will die!

27
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:57,220
Seo Rin.

28
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:03,230
Did Seo Rin know this was going to happen?

29
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:06,430
Is that why Chae Hwa Young
caused the accident on purpose?

30
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,530
How...

31
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:14,610
How could this happen?

32
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,810
Seo Rin!

33
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:24,280
That's right. Seo Rin.

34
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,320
I have to find Seo Rin.

35
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:39,000
If I was admitted as Ma Seo Rin,
then Seo Rin must be here as Oh Jang Mi.

36
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:44,170
Ms. Ma Seo Rin, do you need anything?
Can I help you?

37
00:02:44,900 --> 00:02:48,640
- No.
- I was just about to call your mother.

38
00:02:49,370 --> 00:02:50,740
Please don't call home.

39
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:55,910
- I just came out for a little walk.
- Okay.

40
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,080
By any chance...

41
00:03:01,420 --> 00:03:04,420
Was there another car accident patient...

42
00:03:05,290 --> 00:03:06,390
who was admitted with me?

43
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:09,060
Not in the general wards...

44
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,330
Why do you ask?

45
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,070
It's nothing.

46
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:16,000
Thanks.

47
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,380
If she's not in a general ward...

48
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,120
Jang Mi.

49
00:03:35,220 --> 00:03:36,420
I'll be back tomorrow.

50
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:47,130
Baek Ho.

51
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:49,130
I'm right here.

52
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,240
Jang Mi is right here.

53
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:57,410
(Intensive Care Unit)

54
00:04:00,810 --> 00:04:01,810
Seo Rin.

55
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:03,650
Oh no.

56
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:05,120
Seo Rin.

57
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:24,570
Why did she write my name
and then cross it out like this?

58
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:26,700
It's under today's date too.

59
00:04:27,470 --> 00:04:28,840
Is something supposed to happen today?

60
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:33,610
That's right. Chae Hwa Young
was trying to get rid of me,

61
00:04:34,010 --> 00:04:36,510
but she mistook Seo Rin for me
because she was wearing my clothes.

62
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,650
How can someone be so cruel?

63
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:40,720
How?

64
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,890
(Intensive Care Unit)

65
00:04:55,530 --> 00:04:56,530
I'm so sorry.

66
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,400
I'm so sorry, Seo Rin.

67
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,240
This happened to you instead of me.

68
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,810
That monster, Chae Hwa Young...

69
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:05,540
How could she do this?

70
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:09,080
Seo Rin, I'm so sorry.

71
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:11,020
I'm so sorry.

72
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:22,830
They say that if we try to force
Seo Rin to remember things...

73
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:24,060
or push her emotionally,

74
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,330
it could actually
have negative side effects.

75
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:30,330
So you're Dong Seok's daughter.

76
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:31,500
Hold her, Father.

77
00:05:32,170 --> 00:05:33,970
All right.

78
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:37,680
Oh, you're so pretty. Oh, my sweet girl.

79
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:40,040
It feels like my Dong Seok
has come back to me.

80
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:45,320
The first time I held her in my arms,

81
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:48,520
she was just a little baby
squirming in my arms.

82
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:50,760
And to think she has amnesia now.

83
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:54,990
She must be so scared.

84
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:01,600
Honey.

85
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:07,270
Thankfully, she wasn't badly hurt.
Don't you worry.

86
00:06:07,670 --> 00:06:10,340
I'm sure her memory will come back soon.

87
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:14,080
From the moment she was born,
she was raised as my granddaughter...

88
00:06:14,810 --> 00:06:18,550
and my one and only blood heir
to Dream Group.

89
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:21,390
But now, she doesn't even know
her own name,

90
00:06:21,490 --> 00:06:23,320
or even who she is.

91
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:29,690
So can you imagine
how frustrated and scared she must feel?

92
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,530
Is this too much?

93
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,840
Hey.

94
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:43,370
- What are you doing in here?
- Mom, which one's better? This or this?

95
00:06:43,470 --> 00:06:46,780
Seo Rin would throw a fit if she saw you.
What were you thinking?

96
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:49,350
I heard we should be patient
and wait for her memory to come back.

97
00:06:49,710 --> 00:06:50,750
But these are designer clothes.

98
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,980
It's a shame to let them collect dust
in the closet.

99
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:56,250
This is a limited edition piece
you can't even find in this country.

100
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:58,420
You've got a point.

101
00:07:01,590 --> 00:07:03,530
How much must all of this be worth?

102
00:07:04,030 --> 00:07:07,060
She could open her own makeup store
with all this.

103
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:21,450
Hong Ju, listen. I've been thinking,
and now is the perfect time.

104
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,680
The perfect time for what?

105
00:07:22,810 --> 00:07:26,150
For you to get married
and give the Chairman a grandson.

106
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:27,990
What?

107
00:07:27,990 --> 00:07:29,020
Mom!

108
00:07:29,020 --> 00:07:33,790
The Chairman is heartbroken over Seo Rin.
What better time could there be?

109
00:07:34,530 --> 00:07:38,560
If he's devastated over his granddaughter,
imagine how he'd feel about a grandson.

110
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:43,200
It's because Seo Rin is the only daughter
of the son he tragically lost.

111
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,900
She's his flesh and blood.

112
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:46,940
I'm not even his real daughter.

113
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:48,310
So why would he dote on my child?

114
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:50,780
You think so?

115
00:07:54,010 --> 00:07:55,710
I love this scent.

116
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,280
What are you doing? Aren't you coming?

117
00:07:59,550 --> 00:08:00,550
Right.

118
00:08:29,310 --> 00:08:30,310
Chae Hwa Young.

119
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:33,780
I will never forgive you.

120
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,520
Never!

121
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:50,900
- I'm home.
- Hey. Welcome back.

122
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:52,100
You had a tough day, son?

123
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:57,880
And what's going on with Baek Ho
at the hospital?

124
00:08:58,310 --> 00:09:00,540
- The hospital?
- That's right.

125
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,150
That girl, Oh Jang Mi, you know.

126
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,480
Can you believe it?

127
00:09:04,850 --> 00:09:06,580
It's like she's cursed or something.

128
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,850
- I heard she got into a car accident.
- What?

129
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:12,220
Baek Ho got a call and rushed out,

130
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:14,360
and we haven't heard a word
from him since.

131
00:09:15,230 --> 00:09:17,560
- Was she badly hurt?
- Anyway,

132
00:09:18,430 --> 00:09:22,500
I have a bad feeling
that our families are getting entangled.

133
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:23,700
Tell me about it.

134
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,040
Last time, there was trouble
with her father.

135
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:28,810
What an ill-fated connection.

136
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:31,240
Are you saying
Oh Jang Mi got into a car accident?

137
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:35,680
Director Ma from my company
got into one today as well.

138
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:39,350
Director Ma? You mean Director Ma Seo Rin?

139
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,620
- CEO Chae's daughter?
- Yes.

140
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:44,590
Really? How badly was she hurt?

141
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,420
I don't know the details.

142
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,830
Hwa Young must have been so shocked.

143
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,800
I hope it's nothing serious.

144
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,240
I'm home.

145
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:02,440
Baek Ho, how is Jang Mi? Is she okay?

146
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:26,130
If I'd known something like this
would happen to Jang Mi,

147
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:28,870
I would’ve been nicer to her.

148
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:31,740
I would've made her smile more.

149
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:35,940
I would've made her happier.

150
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,280
I'm so sorry, Jang Mi.

151
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,600
An investigation would be a pain,

152
00:11:00,970 --> 00:11:02,530
so clean up the accident scene.

153
00:11:02,530 --> 00:11:05,300
Yes, I already handled the police,

154
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:08,240
and the Chairman has already spoken
with the hospital director.

155
00:11:08,570 --> 00:11:09,670
Good.

156
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:12,610
If news that the heir to Dream Group...

157
00:11:12,610 --> 00:11:15,810
has amnesia gets leaked to the press,

158
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:17,920
that wouldn't be good
for the Chairman, either.

159
00:11:24,690 --> 00:11:27,260
Right. That's all it comes down to.

160
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:37,270
Seo Rin, get changed. We're going home.

161
00:11:38,970 --> 00:11:39,970
What about my clothes?

162
00:11:40,770 --> 00:11:42,710
They were filthy,
so I threw them out, of course.

163
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,140
Where's my phone?

164
00:11:49,850 --> 00:11:51,520
It was destroyed in the accident,
so I tossed it.

165
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:55,350
- Manager Lee will get you a new one.
- But you could've had the data recovered.

166
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:58,860
What could possibly be on there
that's so important to recover?

167
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:00,990
Just use a new one.

168
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,200
You...

169
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:09,730
Did you get your memory back?

170
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,240
What memory?

171
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:18,340
Ma Seo Rin,
just hang in there a little longer.

172
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:21,980
I'm going to live as you
and crush Chae Hwa Young.

173
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:33,790
(Intensive Care Unit)

174
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:49,140
Tok Hee's gone. Jang Mi's gone.

175
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:51,510
Bok Gil's gone.

176
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:54,680
Where are Ok Hee and Tok Hee?

177
00:12:55,610 --> 00:12:59,520
- What are we going to do? What now?
- How should I know?

178
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,850
Grandma, your bunny's right here.

179
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,890
Ok Hee and Tok Hee...

180
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:05,990
Jang Mi's gone.

181
00:13:06,690 --> 00:13:08,990
Where's Jang Mi? Jang Mi.

182
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:11,360
She's at the hospital.

183
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:13,830
So you'll get to see her in a little bit.

184
00:13:14,370 --> 00:13:15,370
Hey, Yeon Bo Ra.

185
00:13:16,030 --> 00:13:18,670
Jang Mi's hurt.
She's in the hospital because she's hurt.

186
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:20,770
Jang Mi can't be hurt.

187
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,570
Suk Hee is going to the hospital, too.

188
00:13:26,110 --> 00:13:28,350
- Jang Mi is hurt.
- I can't deal with this.

189
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:36,850
Seo Rin,
I'm going to find the evidence you hid...

190
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:38,760
and make Chae Hwa Young pay.

191
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:42,330
I just need to borrow your life
until then.

192
00:13:43,130 --> 00:13:45,400
Ma Seo Rin, you understand, don't you?

193
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:53,300
You silly girl.

194
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:57,880
Your grandfather was so worried,
he didn't sleep a wink all night.

195
00:13:58,780 --> 00:13:59,840
Do you remember...

196
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:02,780
he's the Chairman of Dream Group?

197
00:14:03,850 --> 00:14:06,480
You're his entire world.

198
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:10,720
And you're the heir to Dream Group.

199
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,060
The next chairman.

200
00:14:12,420 --> 00:14:14,430
Ma Seo Rin, did you hear that?

201
00:14:15,190 --> 00:14:18,330
Please wake up soon, for the sake
of your grandfather who loves you dearly.

202
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:19,560
Please.

203
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,970
Just shake this off and wake up healthy.

204
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:24,770
That's why you need to watch how you act.

205
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:28,970
If word gets out that you have amnesia,

206
00:14:30,010 --> 00:14:34,180
the stock price will plummet,
and the press will swarm you.

207
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,950
Shit.

208
00:14:36,950 --> 00:14:37,980
This is boring.

209
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:40,550
I've already got enough stress
to deal with,

210
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,690
and I thought meeting you would be fun.

211
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,790
But no.

212
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:44,820
I was wrong.

213
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,360
Shit.

214
00:14:48,190 --> 00:14:49,190
Shit.

215
00:14:49,430 --> 00:14:52,900
So, when we get home, I want you to do
whatever it takes to get your memory back.

216
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,230
Got it, Seo Rin?

217
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:56,130
Give it a rest.

218
00:14:56,130 --> 00:14:58,440
Shit. You're talking my ear off.

219
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:02,040
So you've lost your memory,

220
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,010
but your attitude is still the same.

221
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:06,980
Chae Hwa Young, you just wait.

222
00:15:07,540 --> 00:15:10,150
I'll be one step ahead of you
and slowly suffocate you.

223
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:13,320
For my mom, my dad, and Seo Rin,

224
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:15,250
I will make sure you answer
for this injustice.

225
00:15:16,050 --> 00:15:17,050
Chae Hwa Young.

226
00:15:17,590 --> 00:15:18,790
I'm going to make your life
a living nightmare.

227
00:15:22,430 --> 00:15:24,860
Oh my. What's with the flowers?

228
00:15:25,830 --> 00:15:29,570
Calla lilies and baby's breath.
They're my favorite.

229
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:34,170
You even know my taste perfectly.
You're so thoughtful.

230
00:15:35,110 --> 00:15:37,440
I just did my homework
on your tastes, Lawyer Han.

231
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:42,080
- You did your homework?
- Let's call it the power of the internet.

232
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:45,820
After all, you're a very famous lawyer.

233
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,790
Thank you.

234
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:51,960
Oh dear, what a shame.

235
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:56,360
- Baek Ho isn't here today either.
- Well...

236
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:59,500
I guess Baek Ho's really busy.

237
00:15:59,930 --> 00:16:02,100
It's so frustrating.

238
00:16:03,170 --> 00:16:05,500
There's this young woman
who runs a side dish shop,

239
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:07,970
and apparently she was
in a car accident yesterday,

240
00:16:08,370 --> 00:16:10,240
so Baek Ho has been a complete wreck.

241
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:14,710
- And he's not even the one who got hurt.
- Wait, the side dish shop?

242
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,610
You mean Oh Jang Mi,
the one Baek Ho likes?

243
00:16:17,950 --> 00:16:20,580
Oh my gosh. You know Oh Jang Mi.

244
00:16:21,990 --> 00:16:26,090
Anyway, he's practically living there
at this point.

245
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:30,290
I feel like we have some bad blood
with her family.

246
00:16:31,430 --> 00:16:34,330
How could she get into
a car accident out of the blue?

247
00:16:34,430 --> 00:16:38,900
- Wait, so the accident was yesterday?
- That's right.

248
00:16:39,370 --> 00:16:42,510
Director Ma Seo Rin
got into a car accident yesterday too.

249
00:16:43,970 --> 00:16:46,010
You should be careful
out there too, Hong Ju.

250
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,610
If you're unlucky,

251
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,550
you can end up in an accident
just like that.

252
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:06,830
It's cold out, Jang Mi.

253
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:10,100
Baek Ho...

254
00:17:19,010 --> 00:17:20,510
You were on the phone
with someone for a while.

255
00:17:21,110 --> 00:17:22,410
Did you think I was them?

256
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:26,150
Yes.

257
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:27,620
So, you're not going to tell me
who that was?

258
00:17:28,150 --> 00:17:29,850
Don't tell me it's a secret from me, too?

259
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:33,760
I'm sorry, but yes.
I'll tell you everything later.

260
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:37,900
Something definitely happened to Jang Mi.

261
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:41,670
Who could she have possibly met
to get into a car accident?

262
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:43,800
Why did she get into a car accident,

263
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:46,440
just like her father?

264
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:54,310
(Intensive Care Unit)

265
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:23,840
Excuse me.

266
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:26,810
Has this person ever been here?

267
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:31,150
Yes, her style was a little different,
though.

268
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:33,120
What? Her style?

269
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:35,050
But the face looks right.

270
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:38,990
How do you remember so clearly?

271
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:41,530
There was that accident that day.

272
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:44,530
Right.

273
00:18:46,130 --> 00:18:47,160
Do you happen to know...

274
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:49,200
who she was meeting here?

275
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:52,000
I think she was supposed to meet someone,

276
00:18:52,670 --> 00:18:54,510
but they seemed to be running late.

277
00:18:54,510 --> 00:18:56,140
She kept waiting,

278
00:18:56,540 --> 00:18:59,110
and I think the accident happened
right after she went outside.

279
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:04,210
- Really?
- As she went out, there was a huge crash.

280
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,820
It was incredibly loud.

281
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:08,490
Thank you for telling me.

282
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:10,820
I hope both of them are okay.

283
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:14,090
What?

284
00:19:15,090 --> 00:19:16,130
Both of them?

285
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:24,940
- You handled the discharge papers, right?
- Yes.

286
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:30,010
Go away!

287
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:35,380
Mom, what's wrong?

288
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:36,480
I'm right here.

289
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:37,780
Mom, calm down.

290
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:39,580
He's scary.

291
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:40,580
Go away!

292
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,590
He's scaring me.

293
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:48,030
My mom recognized Manager Lee.
That's why she was so scared of him.

294
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:50,530
Seo Rin, what's wrong?

295
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:54,400
It's nothing.

296
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:57,370
Don't you even recognize Manager Lee?

297
00:19:58,740 --> 00:19:59,740
Seo Rin.

298
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:02,040
It's me, Manager Lee.

299
00:20:02,970 --> 00:20:06,410
I don't know who you are,
but why do you look so scummy?

300
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:09,680
Who is he? Is he your boyfriend?

301
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,550
Goodness, that's ridiculous.

302
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:13,080
No, Seo Rin.

303
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:16,920
He's my assistant,
and he helps me with my work.

304
00:20:17,390 --> 00:20:18,720
Watch what you say.

305
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:21,530
Shit. What did I say
that was so out of line?

306
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:28,230
I'm starting to think
we're discharging you too early.

307
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:30,700
Seo Rin, do you want to stay
in the hospital a little longer?

308
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,040
Forget it.

309
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:43,110
My daughter Jang Mi is hurting.

310
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,450
Jang Mi is hurting.

311
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:46,850
Jang Mi can't be hurting.

312
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:50,150
Mom, please be quiet. People are staring.

313
00:20:51,050 --> 00:20:52,790
Jang Mi is hurting.

314
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:56,790
(Patient Name: Ma Seo Rin)

315
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:11,480
Mom, please.
Don't cry in front of Jang Mi.

316
00:21:12,180 --> 00:21:15,310
She might seem out of it,
but she can still hear you, okay?

317
00:21:15,410 --> 00:21:17,110
Bok Gil is gone.

318
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:18,380
Tok Hee is gone.

319
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,080
Jang Mi is hurting.

320
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,250
Suk Hee is having a hard time.

321
00:21:22,450 --> 00:21:24,350
Jang Mi is hurting.

322
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:25,920
Then you're not going to go?

323
00:21:26,460 --> 00:21:28,390
You're not going to see Jang Mi?

324
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,900
Jang Mi is hurting.

325
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:48,810
Suk Hee is crying.

326
00:21:48,810 --> 00:21:50,250
Jang Mi is hurting.

327
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,880
Suk Hee is sad.

328
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:56,790
If you're just going to keep crying,
then don't say you want to see her.

329
00:21:57,250 --> 00:21:58,460
I'll just leave without you.

330
00:21:58,820 --> 00:22:00,060
No.

331
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:02,460
I'll see Jang Mi.

332
00:22:03,290 --> 00:22:06,000
I'm scared, but I want to see Jang Mi.

333
00:22:06,460 --> 00:22:08,530
Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

334
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,600
Okay, Mom.

335
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:17,110
Promise me you won't cry in front of her.

336
00:22:17,670 --> 00:22:20,440
Okay. Suk Hee won't cry anymore.

337
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:22,550
Jang Mi can't be hurting.

338
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,550
I promise.

339
00:22:25,450 --> 00:22:28,920
- Jang Mi is hurting. I can't cry.
- Ma'am.

340
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:32,920
Jang Mi is pretty. Jang Mi is hurting.

341
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,590
You should go ahead.

342
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:41,670
- CEO Chae.
- It's Jang Mi.

343
00:22:45,140 --> 00:22:46,140
Mom.

344
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:48,070
Mom.

345
00:22:48,070 --> 00:22:49,070
My mom.

346
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,970
My poor mom.

347
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:55,910
Aren't you Oh Tae Pyung?

348
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:59,280
Yes, but what brings CEO Chae here?

349
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:01,490
There's something I need to tell her.

350
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:03,620
She's busy with an urgent matter
right now.

351
00:23:04,020 --> 00:23:07,290
That man is scary. Suk Hee is scared.

352
00:23:07,990 --> 00:23:10,530
Mom, it's okay.

353
00:23:11,130 --> 00:23:15,800
- Excuse me, but who is that with her?
- Suk Hee is scared.

354
00:23:16,230 --> 00:23:20,240
Jang Mi is pretty. Jang Mi is hurting.
I'm scared. Suk Hee is scared.

355
00:23:20,300 --> 00:23:21,540
I'm scared.

356
00:23:22,670 --> 00:23:23,670
Mom, stop.

357
00:23:23,670 --> 00:23:25,440
It’s very noisy here at the moment,

358
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:28,780
so please say what you need to later
and leave now.

359
00:23:29,350 --> 00:23:31,720
- Yes.
- Suk Hee is scared.

360
00:23:38,050 --> 00:23:39,520
Don't pay them any mind.

361
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:41,290
What a crazy woman.

362
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:43,990
She's probably a patient
from the psychiatric ward.

363
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:47,330
What? A crazy woman?

364
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:49,970
Who do you think made my mom like that?

365
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,500
Let's go.

366
00:23:59,710 --> 00:24:03,080
(Intensive Care Unit)

367
00:24:03,150 --> 00:24:04,210
Jang Mi.

368
00:24:04,850 --> 00:24:06,480
Why are you just lying here like this?

369
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:09,120
You have to wake up.

370
00:24:09,590 --> 00:24:10,890
It's scary.

371
00:24:10,890 --> 00:24:12,690
Ok Hee and Tok Hee are scared.

372
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:31,580
We're home, Seo Rin.

373
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:35,550
Whatever it takes,
you must get your memory back, okay?

374
00:24:36,050 --> 00:24:38,320
Now that I've willingly stepped
into this cursed place,

375
00:24:38,780 --> 00:24:40,180
when I get out of here,

376
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:42,650
I'm dragging you out by the hair,
Chae Hwa Young.

377
00:24:43,350 --> 00:24:45,090
Just you wait, Chae Hwa Young.

378
00:24:45,660 --> 00:24:47,860
Wait here. I'll go get your grandfather.

379
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:58,170
Seo Rin, you're here?

380
00:24:58,870 --> 00:25:01,640
Cross your arms and tilt your head.

381
00:25:01,940 --> 00:25:04,070
And talk to them casually
with an attitude.

382
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:12,620
Seo Rin.

383
00:25:13,450 --> 00:25:15,620
My dear Seo Rin, welcome home.

384
00:25:17,350 --> 00:25:20,520
And with my grandfather,
you have to lay on the charm.

385
00:25:21,060 --> 00:25:22,530
Do that, and you'll be golden.

386
00:25:23,590 --> 00:25:26,960
- Grandfather.
- Yes, it's me. Your grandpa.

387
00:25:28,870 --> 00:25:32,370
Grandfather, Seo Rin will definitely...

388
00:25:32,970 --> 00:25:34,570
wake up.

389
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,310
Seo Rin.

390
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:40,440
You must have been so scared.
But you look...

391
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:43,650
Thank goodness it wasn't any worse.

392
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:47,480
- Who are you? Are you my family?
- My goodness.

393
00:25:48,390 --> 00:25:49,420
It's true.

394
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:53,820
- You don't remember a single thing?
- Yeom San Wol, watch what you say.

395
00:25:54,490 --> 00:25:57,460
I'm sure you were told about
Seo Rin's current condition.

396
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:59,360
Right.

397
00:25:59,860 --> 00:26:01,630
My name is Jin Hong Ju, Seo Rin.

398
00:26:02,470 --> 00:26:03,670
I'm the Chairman's daughter.

399
00:26:04,900 --> 00:26:06,500
Calling me aunt feels a little weird,

400
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,510
so treat me like your sister.

401
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:11,270
Do you remember me?

402
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:14,510
If you're my grandfather's daughter,
why is your last name Jin?

403
00:26:14,950 --> 00:26:16,380
It should be Ma, shouldn't it?

404
00:26:18,450 --> 00:26:21,280
That's because the family registry
hasn't been...

405
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,150
It's okay.

406
00:26:23,150 --> 00:26:26,260
Since she doesn't remember anything,
she must be confused.

407
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:29,360
You must be hungry. Let's go eat.

408
00:26:48,810 --> 00:26:51,280
Mrs. Yang, can I have some more soup?

409
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:53,650
I want a full bowl, and make it extra hot.

410
00:26:53,850 --> 00:26:56,090
That's right.
My Seo Rin needs to eat a lot.

411
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:57,690
That's how you'll get better quickly.

412
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:02,290
Father, it seems Seo Rin
is back to her old self too.

413
00:27:03,230 --> 00:27:05,730
But what's gotten into you?
You used to say soup was fattening,

414
00:27:05,730 --> 00:27:06,800
so you never ate it.

415
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:08,900
None of your business.

416
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,400
Now that you seem to be recovering,

417
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:14,340
you should start watching
your weight again.

418
00:27:17,840 --> 00:27:18,840
Be careful.

419
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:21,810
- Oh my, it's hot!
- It's hot!

420
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,850
Can't you do anything right?

421
00:27:29,450 --> 00:27:31,820
I'm the one who spilled it,
but why did you hit her?

422
00:27:31,990 --> 00:27:34,520
If she had served you properly,
you wouldn't have spilled it.

423
00:27:35,330 --> 00:27:37,730
It's so hot.
I’m worried my leg might be badly burned.

424
00:27:38,800 --> 00:27:39,800
Get out of the way.

425
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:41,360
It's so hot.

426
00:27:46,300 --> 00:27:49,110
Chae Hwa Young.
This is just the beginning.

427
00:27:49,810 --> 00:27:53,480
I'm going to torment you,
grinding you down piece by piece.

428
00:27:54,210 --> 00:27:56,850
Just like when you came into my home
wearing the face of an angel,

429
00:27:57,480 --> 00:28:01,280
I'll wear the mask of Ma Seo Rin
and give you a taste of your own medicine.

430
00:28:21,870 --> 00:28:23,410
(The First Man)

431
00:28:23,470 --> 00:28:25,510
Chairman, I deserve to die
for what I've done.

432
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:29,180
Now, I’m going to catch
Seo Rin's hit-and-run driver myself.

433
00:28:29,210 --> 00:28:30,450
Director Ma Seo Rin.

434
00:28:30,850 --> 00:28:33,050
I know her. She looks just like Jang Mi.

435
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,850
I'm starting to wonder
if it was the same accident.

436
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:37,250
Excuse me, were there any other patients
brought in besides her?

437
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:39,860
We'll find out
once we check Seo Rin's phone.

438
00:28:40,420 --> 00:28:42,730
I have to find that phone
before Chae Hwa Young does.

439
00:28:43,690 --> 00:28:46,900
Just you wait, Chae Hwa Young.
I'm going to put you through torment.

440
00:28:48,530 --> 00:28:50,530
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
